        "content": "**Feldmapping Formular → SharePoint:**\n\nThema          → Title + field_1\nPost_Typ       → field_2\nContent_Brief  → field_3\nDatum          → Ver_x00f6_ffentlichungsdatum\nUhrzeit        → field_5\nStatus         → field_6 = 'Entwurf' (auto)\nHashtag_Thema  → field_7\nBild_Dateiname → field_8  (optional, sonst von WF-02 generiert)\nFreigabe_Person→ field_11\nKommentare     → field_13\n\n**Felder von Downstream-Workflows befüllt:**\nfield_8  – Bild_Dateiname  (WF-02 v18.3)\nfield_10 – Caption         (WF-02 v18.3)\nfield_12 – Instagram_Post_ID (WF-03 v6)\n\nSite-GUID: c74040a2-0d6b-4385-b514-fbd9830a56ac\nList-GUID: d17a6a6f-e6ef-457d-a2a9-4c30ea56120f\nCredential: PF Microsoft SharePoint",
